## n8n@0.210.0 View the [commits](https://github.com/n8n-io/n8n/compare/n8n@0.209.4...n8n@0.210.0) for this version.
**Release date:** 2023-01-05 This release introduces two major new features: log streaming and security audits. It also contains node enhancements, bug fixes, and performance improvements.
